            <li><a href="#tab-5">Deadlines and Pricing<span>Early bird gets it</span></a></li>
            <li><a href="#tab-6">Volunteer<span>Karma's a five letter word</span></a></li>
            <li><a href="#tab-7">Charity<span>Run FOR Something</span></a></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tab-content left">
